### Key Learnings
- Effective landing pages focus on one primary objective.
- Headlines should clearly communicate the value proposition.
- Customer-centric messaging performs better than company-centric messaging.
- Remove distractions that take users away from the primary call-to-action.
- Build credibility using testimonials, case studies, and measurable results.
- Maintain consistency between ad copy and landing page messaging.
- Optimize pages based on user behavior and conversion data.
- Regular experimentation is essential for improving conversion rates.

